      <name>Sea Kobold</name>
      <advantage>All: +2 dice to Nautical Mechanic</advantage>
      <disadvantage>Whenever a follower of Sea Kobold is in danger (in reality or only in his imagination) or he has to stay on or in a vehicle for a prolonged time (be it cars, ships, planes or trains), he must make a CHA + WIL (3) test. Should he fail, he is convinced he saw the Sea Kobold, resulting in him running scared and trying to flee, as well as trying to convince other characters that their plans will lead to a bad end.</disadvantage>
      <bonus>
        <specificskill>
          <name>Nautical Mechanic</name>
          <bonus>2</bonus>
        </specificskill>
      </bonus>
